{"id":4726,"date":"2019-11-25T16:22:19","date_gmt":"2019-11-25T21:22:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/farah-louiza-mahdjoub-se-merite-la-5e-place-au-concours-philosopher-2019\/"},"modified":"2024-10-15T09:36:28","modified_gmt":"2024-10-15T13:36:28","slug":"farah-louiza-mahdjoub-se-merite-la-5e-place-au-concours-philosopher-2019","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/farah-louiza-mahdjoub-se-merite-la-5e-place-au-concours-philosopher-2019\/","title":{"rendered":"Farah Louiza Mahdjoub se m\u00e9rite la 5e place au concours Philosopher 2019"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Le <a href=\"https:\/\/www.concoursphilosopher.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">concours <em>Philosopher<\/em> <\/a>a \u00e9t\u00e9 cr\u00e9\u00e9 en 1988 et vise \u00e0 pousser encore plus loin la r\u00e9flexion des \u00e9tudiants et des \u00e9tudiantes de niveau coll\u00e9gial sur des questions philosophiques. Ceux et celles qui souhaitent participer ont environ 5 mois pour r\u00e9diger une dissertation philosophique de 2 000 mots sur un th\u00e8me pr\u00e9d\u00e9termin\u00e9. Parmi les th\u00e8mes des \u00e9ditions pr\u00e9c\u00e9dentes, on retrouve des questions telles que \u00abLa beaut\u00e9 sauvera-t-elle le monde?\u00bb, ou encore \u00abQuels jugements porter sur le capitalisme?\u00bb.<\/p>\n<p>Pour l&rsquo;\u00e9dition 2019, le th\u00e8me \u00e9tait: \u00abComment vivre avec l&rsquo;intelligence artificielle?\u00bb et le jury a re\u00e7u plus d&rsquo;une centaine de textes!<\/p>\n<p>Lors du gala de remise des prix qui s&rsquo;est d\u00e9roul\u00e9 le 21 novembre dernier, Farah Louiza Mahdjoub, dipl\u00f4m\u00e9e du c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent en <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/programmes\/sciences-humaines\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sciences humaines<\/a>, a remport\u00e9 la 5<sup>e<\/sup> place pour son texte intitul\u00e9 \u00abUne guerre intelligente?\u00bb.<\/p>\n<p>F\u00e9licitations \u00e0 la jeune philosophe, ainsi qu&rsquo;\u00e0 Pierre-Alexandre Fradet qui a agi \u00e0 titre d&rsquo;enseignant-tuteur dans le cadre de ce concours!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>F\u00e9licitations \u00e0 Farah Louiza Mahdjoub qui s&rsquo;est m\u00e9rit\u00e9e la cinqui\u00e8me place lors du concours intercoll\u00e9gial de dissertations philosophiques Philosopher 2019!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":4727,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[196,2611],"etiquette-interne":[2301,2323,2337],"class_list":["post-4726","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-honneurs","sujet-actualite-reussite-etudiante","etiquette-interne-honneurs","etiquette-interne-philosophie","etiquette-interne-reussite-etudiante"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:26:27","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4726","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4726"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4726\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4969,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4726\/revisions\/4969"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www